{"type":"article_comment","id":21463,"parentType":"article","parentId":2861,"uid":4630,"contents":"對了，我想到除了深綠色，淺藍色也是一個很好的選項。駐南韓的聯合國軍就使用淺藍底的聯合國旗，根據聯合國安理會第82、83、和84號決議，組織全世界（除蘇聯外）的聯合國成員國集體出兵倒共。當然這個顏色有全球主義的色彩。（當然，如同某些人所講，深綠色也有法西斯的色彩。）<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/ziVY1Ru.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ziVY1Ru.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/ziVY1Ru.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/P2L24ZT.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/P2L24ZT.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/P2L24ZT.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2020-08-09","agreeCount":0,"discussionCount":0}